nted risk assessments from all perspectives. Final decision based on safety > security > availability priority."},"continuous_improvement_and_updates":{"why":"Update qualification processes must evolve with emerging threats and technology changes.","update_process":[{"step":"Threat intelligence monitoring","description":"Subscribe to ICS-CERT alerts and vendor bulletins to identify new vulnerability patterns requiring process adjustments."},{"step":"Post-implementation review","description":"After major updates, document lessons learned about qualification effectiveness."}],"lessons_learned":"Example: After a 2022 gas pipeline incident, we added requirement to test updates against all protocol variants used in field deployments, not just reference configurations."}},"standard_compliance":"IEC 62443-4-1","last_updated":"2023-11-15"} 
